1126
01:10:01,201 --> 01:10:03,663
<i>El FBI ha arrestado a
cuatro hombres blancos...</i>

1127
01:10:03,703 --> 01:10:04,664
<i>acusados de arrojar una...</i>

1128
01:10:04,704 --> 01:10:06,540
<i>bomba incendiaria
en un autobús de...</i>

1129
01:10:06,581 --> 01:10:08,751
